title: Bishops Are Better Than Knights? - Nana Dzagnidze Wins Women's World Blitz Championship 2017

The "King Salman World Blitz & Rapid Championships 2017" in Riyadh from December 26th to 30th. The first five rounds of the rapid tournament take place on December 26th. A record $2 million prize fund has attracted most of the world's best players.

Nana Dzagnidze vs Tingjie Lei
World Blitz Championship (Women) (2017), Riyadh KSA, rd 10, Dec-29 
Nimzowitsch-Larsen Attack: General (A06)

1. Nf3 d5 2. b3 Nf6 3. Bb2 Nbd7 4. e3 e6 5. d4 Bd6 6. Bd3 O-O 7. O-O c5 8. Nbd2 b6 9. Ne5 Bb7 10. f4 cd4 11. ed4 Ne4 12. Qe2 f5 13. Ne4 fe4 14. Bb5 Ne5 15. fe5 Bc7 16. Ba3 Rf5 17. Qg4 Qg5 18. Qg5 Rg5 19. Bd7 Rg6 20. Be7 Ba6 21. Rf4 h6 22. Re1 Kh7 23. Re3 Bc8 24. Be8 Rg5 25. Bg5 hg5 26. Rf8 g6 27. Rh3 Kg7 28. Rfh8
